I"ž,<h1 class="disable-paragraph-marker" id="technical-information">Technical Information</h1>

<p>The Library of Christ Mind Teachings is a set of static sites generated
by <a href="https://jekyllrb.com/">Jekyll</a>, hosted by <a href="app.netlify.com">Netlify</a>
and extended by APIâ€™s implemented on <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/">AWS</a>. The
software is open source and available on
<a href="https://github.com/Christ-Mind-Teachings">GitHub</a>.</p>

<p>The Library includes the following components.</p>

