<h1 id="hosting">Hosting</h1>

<p>The Library is hosted by <a href="https://www.netlify.com/"> Netlify </a> with a free Open Source Team Plan,
thank you Netlify!</p>

<h2 id="amazon-web-services">Amazon Web Services</h2>

<p>Amazon Route 53 is our Domain Name Registrar, audio files are stored in
an S3 bucket, DynamoDB is our database, and API Gateway and Lambda
provide APIâ€™s for search, bookmarks, and user functions.</p>

